Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終的舞臺在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------新OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:38.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:45.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:01:01.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:11.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:23.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:34.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:40.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:46.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:50.62,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:53.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:38.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:45.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在倒錯的精神世界中相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:01:01.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們眼裡的世界總是相互顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:11.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾乎要被認定為是無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:23.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口淌淚的眼眸 在內心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:34.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的兩人來不及結合便聽到離別的倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:40.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:46.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們像漸趨衰老的動物一樣相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:50.62,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:53.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在倒錯的精神世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想細細體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==================OP=================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:09.40,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(719,400)}復活之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這音色 這旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太適合於最終樂章了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續吧 繼續奏響吧 Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體哪裡還藏有如此強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優雅而纖細
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又灼熱而激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢雄渾地響徹心底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特在不穿Element制服的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過強行露出自己的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使自己的感官得到進一步的加強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肉體所受的打擊應該相當巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那簡直就是捨身戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:03:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我的靈魂奉上最精彩的獨奏協奏曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:03:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(577,440)\fs24}Kadenz
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我所看到的不是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪第一次相遇時沒有聞到你的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和我有著相同的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我原本是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 那個只能任由命運擺佈的阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在你也沒什麼改變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那個一到關鍵時刻就束手無策的膽小鬼阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又有什麼了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後都救不了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去Altair都做些什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然穿越了次元 但我和母親失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候我遇到了未影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 半身的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗之阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫做神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起你就叫神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了記憶 由未影一手撫養
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 母親的事已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟連不明來歷的父親也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說重要的氣味是唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有心愛的臭女人的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的希爾菲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把御子乃交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真弱真弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 為什麼你們兩人要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼終於覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你是怎麼地不軟弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次元量子反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在湖泊一帶的地底下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個標誌是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion居然產生了共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從1萬2千年前的太古傳來的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是傳說中的神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼終於現身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你啊 希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越了1萬2千年的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在終於能夠殺死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要殺掉御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我要殺掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦地 激烈地 冷酷地 無數次地殺死她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺掉你 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他之後 讓我們好好地廝殺至天明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你碰她一根指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次元量子等級正持續上升
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的 這是真傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說終於化為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正身處在如此偉大的歷史瞬間面前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 明明到了這麼重要的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是傳說之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動總司令 您什麼時候回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打情罵俏 犬亦不理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧 這是1萬2千年前就已經決定好的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和希爾菲結合的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你怎麼掙扎也無法戰勝命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和希爾菲正因是被命運所指引著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使身處不同的星球也能相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有著能跨越命運的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有翅膀 不用以飛翔也是毫無意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能飛起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 飛起來給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你不可以繼續傷害阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑臉太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我越來越想殺死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑吧 繼續笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續吧 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒事啊 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔才是 難道說你是擔心我才回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡 我終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正重要的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:11:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我的約定還沒有兌現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 你和我的約定還沒有兌現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看到你們兩人互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要了斷什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是因為命運才追求御子乃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不要讓我一再說明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管御子乃是不是希爾菲轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和1萬2千年前的命運也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對現在的…現在的御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 此時此刻 這一瞬間的 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在這裡較量一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的命運和你的癡情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個更加強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會輸個你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點 還差一點我所追求的旋律就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你怎麼了 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎 摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這音色很美妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特的生命等級異常低下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續進行戰鬥會危及性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換Element
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由柚葉替換修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:15:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能戰鬥 還差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一步 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換Element 快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉·蘇爾 參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion的高次元量子反應已經超出了檢測範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動 你到底想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切不都已經顯示在創聖之書上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話只能由高尚的生命撰寫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 以流蕩著的血液為墨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有阻止的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止還是慫恿都是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:16:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合十的雙手之間到底有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中什麼也沒有 只有無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 無雖無 但又不盡為無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正負的兩種力量相互抵消產生出無的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·鈴白的連接之力亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光與暗 聖與邪 善與惡 還有陰與陽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人封閉著的記憶被打開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從虛無中誕生的無限力量開始運動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是現在新的一頁即將翻開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼在我的懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門打開了 我們也快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台Abductor以及神話型Aquarion沖入了次元之門中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 克蕾亞理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再一次 再一次讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的會沒命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你收留的我來到Neo DEAVA時就已經明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一天遲早會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請答應我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子完成以後也讓我聽一聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台Vector闖入次元之門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視器畫面被中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃和神樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奏響最後的樂曲之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先奪回神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有兩人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來跟你們合體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡 你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 這就是我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運合體 GO Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂在顫動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion SPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磔刑斬擊劍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(424,439)}CRUCIFXION SWORD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元之門開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mithra Gnis入侵我領域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體中有Rare·Igler反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓神樂如此執著的Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的一定是真實的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓神樂獨佔真實的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從世界各地傳來地殼變動和氣候異常的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於解除了神話型Aquarion的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:22:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair和Vega之間保持至今的平衡已經被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話型Aquarion被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和修雷特他們的通信也依然斷絕著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊就沒有什麼辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在放棄還太早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼只有被選中的Element才能操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機終於來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你履行約定的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草綠色頭髮的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.86,0:24:25.28,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(271,400)}神話旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我告訴你我喜歡的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點點的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.23,0:24:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的東西也告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是欺騙 背叛 和那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================ED=====================
